title: BONUS: Introducing Dead Ass with Khadeen and Devale Ellis
description:
Here’s a new podcast for you: Each week Khadeen and Devale Ellis spread love the Brooklyn way on their show, Dead Ass. As a millennial married couple, they reveal personal truths, share opinions, and inspire us to level up in our own lives by giving some advice — but no matter what you hear they will always keep it 100. Dead Ass is out NOW - listen wherever you get your podcasts.

Support the show
